<p> Halal meals are available at all sites. But the city will expand 
Halal meal access at 32 sites in neighborhoods with large Muslim 
populations during the month of Ramadan, which starts Thursday. 
Initially, the 32 sites weren’t listed online Thursday morning.</p>
<p> “We have to be smart about getting information out in real time,” de
 Blasio said of the flub. “In the rush of events here, sometimes things 
are missed.”</p>
